    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/4e1e4188a73a08ee38d82ff6607d5f08.avif?t=1763942069\" width=760 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/3b4b59aa729613d9bc02399747f7c7a0.avif?t=1763942069\" width=925 height=165 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/dcde8466d7b7f2120c4c14ef5db47265.poster.avif?t=1763942069\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/dcde8466d7b7f2120c4c14ef5db47265.webm?t=1763942069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/dcde8466d7b7f2120c4c14ef5db47265.mp4?t=1763942069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have only one type of move - rotating the 6 hexes around the tile you click on. Use it to overcome a variety of challenges, avoid traps and slay your enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/181de5e4aa694cd2978137516a6118b9.avif?t=1763942069\" width=925 height=165 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/592d87add52328c50072211d272fd794.poster.avif?t=1763942069\" width=800 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/592d87add52328c50072211d272fd794.webm?t=1763942069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/592d87add52328c50072211d272fd794.mp4?t=1763942069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smell trash, play with flies and eat cheese. Roleplay as the infamous <strong>generic rat</strong> and take on a huge journey through your home sewers and meet one of the most goofy rats you could imagine.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/17b02449bc6d88ec6475fe9e38fa64b1.avif?t=1763942069\" width=925 height=165 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inconceivable Rat Endeavour</strong> is mainly a puzzle game. However, it borrows handsomely from other genres and sprinkles it on top of the core mechanics, achieving unique, unconventional and  silly gameplay. The game takes you on an endeavour, where you'll constantly see new things and travel forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338180/extras/9208f97bfd5293f2fe81e351f0c6ff46.avif?t=1763942069\" width=760 height=240 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >at least one rat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >exactly 23 types of cheese</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >it's literally a game about a rat</p></li></ul>",
